.TH LOA-LANGUAGE 1 "2026-03-15" "Library Of Alexandria" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
language \- Set language for one book
.SH SYNOPSIS
alexandria> language
.SH DESCRIPTION
.TP
Prompts for a book reference (ID, ISBN, title, or author) and updates its language.
.TP
Supported language values are: German, English, French, Japanese.
.TP
Changes are saved immediately.
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
alexandria> language
.TP
alexandria> (reference: b0002, language: French)
